  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with supine dependent Obstructive Sleep Apnea (OSA) after Mandibular
             Advancement Device (MAD) Therapy: Apnea Hypopnea Index (AHI) supine ≥ 2x AHI non
             supine

          -  5 &lt; AHI &lt; 50/h sleep on polysomnography (PSG) with MAD in situ

          -  ≥ 20% supine position during PSG with the MAD in situ

          -  AHI non-supine &lt; 10/h en AHI supine ≥ 10/h on PSG with MAD in situ

          -  Unchanged Body Mass Index (BMI)(BMI ± 1 kg/m²) at moment of inclusion compared to BMI
             at baseline PSG

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  age &lt; 18 years
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
